        ISPICKVAL ( SBQQ__Quote__r.SBQQ__Type__c , "Amendment") ,

        OR(
            QuantityOfNewSilverGoldLinesRollup__c < 1 ,
            ISBLANK( QuantityOfNewSilverGoldLinesRollup__c )

    IF(                        /* Initial TRUE IF Function -- Discount Schedule */
        AND(

        ( Calculated_MRR__c - BLANKVALUE( SBQQ__UpgradedSubscription__r.Zuora_MRR__c , 0) ) * 12 , /* This calculates ARR directly since tiered products Net Price is blended */
        IF(                                                            /* BAESIC-584 Moved this IF Function up from Main Else portion to Fix SH/AIOPS No Change NNARR bug  */
            AND(

                fml_SubscriptionQuantity__c = SBQQ__Quantity__c  ,
                OR(

                )             /* BAESIC-373  By setting this to all use cases fixes issue for AiOps No Qty Change on Amend Should = 0 ARR input to POT Calcs */
            ) ,                    
            0,
            Order_Form_Quantity__c * NetPriceMonthly__c * 12 
        )

            AND(

                QL_Quantity_Exempted__c
            ),
            1,             /* Stakeholder on Amend upsell will use Qty 1, addressed here */
            SBQQ__Quantity__c    /* All other Use Cases here, including New Business/Renewals/etc  */    
        )
